---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Why Choose Us"
  description="Discover why Meadowlark Endocrinology offers the best personalized hormone and endocrine care for you and your family."
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
      Why Choose Meadowlark Endocrinology?
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      At Meadowlark Endocrinology, we believe that exceptional healthcare begins with a
      genuine partnership between physician and patient. Our membership-based practice
      allows us to provide the personalized, unhurried care you deserve.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-primary">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-3">Personalized Attention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          With a limited patient panel, we spend more time with each patient. No rushed
          appointments, no feeling like just another number. Your concerns are heard,
          your questions are answered.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-primary">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-3">Direct Access</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Reach your endocrinologist directly when you need guidance. Same-day or
          next-day appointments are often available, and we respond promptly to your
          messages and calls.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-primary">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-3">Comprehensive Care</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We treat the full spectrum of endocrine conditions including diabetes,
          thyroid disorders, metabolic syndrome, osteoporosis, pituitary disorders,
          and hormonal imbalances.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-primary">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-3">Modern Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We combine evidence-based medicine with the latest advances in endocrinology.
          Our secure patient portal keeps you connected and informed about your health
          journey.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="bg-accent/10 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-4">
        Conditions We Treat
      </h2>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Type 1 & Type 2 Diabetes
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Thyroid Disorders
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Metabolic Syndrome
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Osteoporosis
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Adrenal Disorders
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Pituitary Conditions
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> PCOS
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-primary">&#10003;</span> Hormonal Imbalances
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href="/become-a-member"
        class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-md transition-colors"
      >
        Start Your Journey Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
